# This text file should explain how to deploy your website.

# You should write detailed description on:

# 1. All the packages you need to install
# 2. How to configure various servers (e.g., Nginx, Apache, etc)

To deploy the website, you must install packages in the frontend, this is done by doing:
"cd course-project/frontend" followed by "npm install", then to run the frontend, execute "npm run dev"
For the backend, execute the following:
"cd course-project/backend" followed by "npm install" as well as "npx prisma migrate dev", then to run the backend, execute "npm run dev"

